{"tid":775178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞航將香港區旗變五星旗","createTime":"2018-08-11T03:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T03:44:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31d9f44c93f892fc4ce492c8b4596f5d61b0eb24","tid":775178,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180811/20473910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F20473910&d=QBSkKEYAiAUBAIaFAeT1IIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=9d7de958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F20473910&h=a1a620fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180811/20473910</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月11日 <br />\n<br />\n瑞航將香港區旗變五星旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180811/large/11la6p61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F11la6p61.jpg&h=731bd107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■瑞士航空網站上，香港的區旗亦被改為中國的五星紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國近日施加政治壓，逼各國際航空公司將網站上對台灣的稱謂更改成中國台灣。有市民發現瑞士航空網站上香港的區旗亦被改為中國的五星紅旗，質疑瑞士航空為了中國市場而有意貶低香港特區的法定地位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指為討好中國<br />\n<br />\n英文網媒Hong Kong Free Press報道，有網民發現瑞士航空網站上，選擇香港地區，及香港預訂機票專頁，均使用了中國國旗，即五星紅旗，而非香港特區法定的紫荊花區旗。該網民向航空公司作出投訴，指摘瑞航不理香港有本身的法定區旗，改用中國國旗，是貶低香港的地位，令人質疑瑞士航空此舉是要討好中國市場，為了政治及利益而犧牲公正及事實。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，未知瑞士航空何時開始用中國國旗代表香港，而報道引述瑞士航空回應稱，有關做法是符合國際慣例，包括世界銀行的規定。<br />\n<br />\n但Hong Kong Free Press向世界銀行查詢，獲回覆稱並無相關規定。翻查中國各航空公司的網頁，香港地區均採用特區區旗。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向瑞士航空查詢，發言人回覆稱，瑞士航空一向慣例是只使用國旗，由於香港特區是中國一部份，所以使用中國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n緻藍天單位石屎藏發泡膠<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n首7個月41遇襲　定罪率不足兩成　 緝打車長疑犯　九巴無提供八達通紀錄"},{"pid":"91d5a13fa46a4aed7276aae2e87742f5993f9a02","tid":775178,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"抽氣扇會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2c728f9f4d9606822480ddae91349464cc4c19","tid":775178,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"痴線，不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0910aa81eb4cb11034bd06470f2d7a2ea10291","tid":775178,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"台灣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d50b88b0cf310a9b98dfd4f7724ed4247d3bfcd","tid":775178,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母瑞士！地球上不是只有國才有旗！<br />\n地區都有旗！瑞士正一白人中共產黨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40ba07acc46b3c53c498205819f99e22aaf1687","tid":775178,"uid":40216,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"建議將瑞士國旗變成德國/歐盟國旗"},{"pid":"a82b022a8971eaa467a8f1d016fc06d0235e063b","tid":775178,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0910aa81eb4cb11034bd06470f2d7a2ea10291","tid":775178,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"台灣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"搵唔到"},{"pid":"ad9a44e198e992512f805def09d4d5c6883f4841","tid":775178,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e40ba07acc46b3c53c498205819f99e22aaf1687","tid":775178,"uid":40216,"